{"type":"entity","name":"Code.Config.Chatmodes.Module_DevTeam_chatmode","entityType":"Module","observations":["DevTeam chatmode configuration with 11-phase workflow and VMP integration. Core principles: memory-first, codegraph-driven, structured phases, CEPH evolution, quality gates (100% test pass), vertical mode protocol for interruptions.","VMP section: Stack-based workflow management with PUSH/POP operations. Auto-detection triggers (5 patterns), max depth 5, breadcrumb navigation with ← arrows. Unified template handles user questions and agent blockers via ORIGIN field differentiation.","Modified 2025-10-13: Replaced IRP with condensed VMP (60→18 lines). Added STACK optional field to completion format. Updated Error Recovery with VMP routing (TEST failure→PUSH DEBUG, blocker→PUSH appropriate phase, max depth→POP_ALL). Updated Communication section (Horizontal/Vertical flows).","upd:2025-10-13,refs:0"]}
{"type":"entity","name":"Code.Config.Instructions.Module_standards","entityType":"Module","observations":["Project standards configuration defining memory system (4-layer), documentation templates (ARCH/BLUEPRINT/TECH/GUIDE), quality standards (code <500 lines, testing 100% pass), codegraph standards, communication standards (phase indicators, status format).","Modified 2025-10-13: Added VMP format requirements section with STACK optional field. Examples: '🔄 VMP PUSH | STACK: 🏗️ ARCHITECT ← 🔬 ANALYZE (depth:2)' for blockers, '🔄 VMP | STACK: 💻 IMPLEMENT (depth:0)' for user interruptions. Stack notation uses ← arrows for breadcrumbs.","upd:2025-10-13,refs:0"]}
{"id":"Code.Module.generator","type":"Module","name":"generator.py","content":"Report generation module with node-based grouping, PDF anchor bookmarks, DOCX TOC, intelligent line wrapping. Key methods: extract_node_from_filename(regex), group_logs_by_node(Dict structure), wrap_long_lines(textwrap), generate_pdf(reportlab with anchors), generate_docx(python-docx with headings). TYPE_ORDER constant for file type ordering. Try/except import for utils.file_utils compatibility.","relations":["IMPORTS:utils.file_utils","IMPORTS:reportlab.platypus","IMPORTS:docx","BELONGS_TO:src"],"metadata":{"upd":"2025-10-13","refs":0}}
{"id":"Code.Tests.Unit.Module_test_report_generation_improvements","type":"Module","name":"test_report_generation_improvements.py","content":"Comprehensive test suite for report generation features. 6 test classes (NodeExtraction, LogGrouping, LineWrapping, PDFGeneration, DOCXGeneration, Integration) with 24 tests total. Validates regex patterns, dictionary grouping, textwrap logic, reportlab integration, python-docx integration, end-to-end workflows. Uses tempfile for isolation, pytest fixtures for test data.","relations":["IMPORTS:src.generator","IMPORTS:pytest","IMPORTS:tempfile","BELONGS_TO:tests/unit"],"metadata":{"upd":"2025-10-13","refs":0}}
